1
00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:02,630
What? You're still awake?

2
00:00:02,630 --> 00:00:05,210
With you touching me like that,
of course I'd wake up.

3
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:09,090
Were you pretending to be asleep?

4
00:00:09,090 --> 00:00:10,390
What do you think?

5
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:11,850
Tell me!

6
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:13,720
Since when were you awake?

7
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:16,100
Stop it.
Don't you have to get up early tomorrow?

8
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:17,350
We should get some sleep.

9
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:20,980
Yeah, I know, but...

10
00:00:24,110 --> 00:00:25,820
We didn't finish what we started.

11
00:00:28,150 --> 00:00:29,780
It's fine. Next time.

12
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:31,160
No.

13
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:33,580
Who knows when next time will be?

14
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:57,520
The alarm is going off.

15
00:00:57,720 --> 00:00:58,850
Mmh...

16
00:01:00,310 --> 00:01:01,940
Mmh... Mmh...

17
00:01:01,940 --> 00:01:05,070
No, you can't!
Get up!

18
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,730
You have to go to work. Hurry!

19
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:07,820
Whoa!

20
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,200
Ah! Ha!

21
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:11,990
I'm awake!

22
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,580
Hehehe.
